<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Words Only in SOWPODS — Valid Internationally But Not in TWL</h1>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">Published June 15, 2026 · 5 min read</p>

<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">SOWPODS contains roughly 40,000 words that North American players can't use. These SOWPODS-exclusive words include British spellings, Commonwealth slang, archaic English, and international vocabulary. If you play internationally or online with SOWPODS enabled, knowing these exclusives gives you a massive tactical advantage.</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Dictionary Comparison</h2>

<div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
  <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-center">
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">~280K</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">SOWPODS total words</p></div>
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">~187K</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">TWL total words</p></div>
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">~40K</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">SOWPODS-exclusive</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

